<sect1 id="dir_7002044952ee345c222d895bec1a9397_1autotoc_md459">
<title>helios::engine::modules::spatial</title><para>Spatial data management for game entities.</para>
<para>This module provides components and systems for managing the spatial state of GameObjects, including transforms, translations, rotations, and scales.</para>
